items.name: USA-Housing-Case-Study
items.description: A comprehensive exploratory data analysis (EDA) on the USA Housing dataset to identify the key factors influencing home prices. This project includes visualizations, statistical insights, and a correlation study to uncover patterns in housing market data. Ideal for beginners in data science and a great foundation for building predictive models.
